      <title>美联储的‘常态’是什么样的？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-19/what-does-normal-look-like-for-the-federal-reserve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本周杰克逊霍尔经济研讨会之前，ADP 首席经济学家兼 ESG 官 Nela Richardson 表示，美联储需要“遏制对经济衰退的恐慌，并告诉我们正常情况是什么样的。”（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-19/what-does-normal-look-like-for-the-federal-reserve</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
