      <title>PGIM 正在筹集私人信贷基金以与大公司竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/pgim-to-compete-with-blackstone-ares-for-larger-private-credit-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，PGIM Inc. 正在为更大规模的直接贷款交易筹集私人信贷基金，以与黑石公司和 Ares Management Corp. 等公司竞争。]]></description>
